album.title: Now That's What I Call Music, Vol. 77

wiki.summary: "positions" is the lead single and twelfth track from Ariana Grande's sixth studio album Positions. It was released on October 23, 2020 through Republic Records. The song is a midtempo track that blends pop and R&B elements with trap beats, plucked guitar, and violin. Lyrically, the song finds Grande expressing her willingness to take on various roles for her romantic partner. Upon release, the track debuted at number one on the Billboard Hot 100, becoming her fifth chart-topping single on the chart. Read more on Last.fm.
